<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Hotels</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper min-h-[100vh] flex flex-col">
      <!-- @import ../components/header.kit -->
      <div class="text-gray-800">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-3xl mt-10 mb-8 font-bold">Privacy policy</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="px-8">
          <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
            <strong class="font-bold text-xl">Introduction</strong><br />
            Your privacy is important to us. This statement outlines what data
            we collect, how we use it, and how we protect your information.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-1 text-xl"><strong class="font-bold">Data We Collect</strong></p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-disc pl-8">
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Personal Data</strong>: Name, email address, and contact
              details.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you use the
              website.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Cookies and Tracking</strong>: Use of cookies and similar
              technologies.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-1 text-xl"><strong class="font-bold">How We Use Your Data</strong></p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-disc pl-8">
            <li>To improve the website and enhance user experience.</li>
            <li>To provide information and offers, subject to your consent.</li>
            <li>For analytical and marketing purposes.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
            <strong class="font-bold text-xl">Sharing Your Data</strong><br />
            We may share data with third parties, such as service providers and
            partners, but only as necessary to deliver our services.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-1 text-xl"><strong class="font-bold">Your Rights</strong></p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-disc pl-8">
            <li><strong class="font-bold">Access</strong>: The right to access your data.</li>
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Correction</strong>: The right to correct inaccurate data.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Deletion</strong>: The right to have your data deleted.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="font-bold">Restriction</strong>: The right to restrict data
              processing.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
            <strong class="font-bold text-xl">Changes to the Privacy Policy</strong><br />
            This privacy policy may be updated. In case of significant changes,
            we will notify you accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- @import ../components/footer.kit -->
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
